process.on('uncaughtException', (err) => { console.error(err); process.exit(1); });
```
Never return `err.message` or `err.stack` to the client — it leaks implementation details.

## 2. No security headers

Add `helmet` to set sane defaults (HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options, frame-ancestors, etc.):
```js
