app.disable('x-powered-by'); // also hides Express fingerprint
app.use(helmet());
```

## 3. No rate limiting / DoS protection

Add `express-rate-limit` (or similar) at least on public endpoints:
```js
const rateLimit = require('express-rate-limit');
app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 60_000, max: 100 }));
```

## 4. No body parsing limits (forward-looking)

When you add POST/PUT, always bound payloads:
```js
