## 3. Missing security headers
Add `helmet` to set sensible defaults (CSP, HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options, frame-ancestors, etc.):

```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');   // also manually remove the fingerprint
app.use(helmet());
