- [ ] Set explicit body-parser size limits.
- [ ] Validate all `req.query`, `req.params`, `req.body` with a schema (zod/joi).
- [ ] Wrap async handlers so rejections reach the error middleware.
- [ ] Use an allowlist serializer for user-facing objects.
- [ ] Read port/config from env; validate at startup.
- [ ] Handle `unhandledRejection`, `uncaughtException`, and graceful shutdown.
- [ ] Ensure logs never include secrets or PII.

