| Concern | Mitigation |
|---|---|
| Stack trace / internals leakage | Generic 500 response, log details server-side only |
| Injection via unchecked input | Validate/coerce with `zod` (or `joi`, `ajv`) before use |
| Unbounded payloads (DoS) | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Abuse / brute force | `express-rate-limit` |
| Common web attacks (XSS, clickjacking, MIME sniffing) | `helmet` sets safe default headers |
| Fingerprinting | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| Open CORS by default | Add `cors` with an explicit allowlist if cross-origin is needed |
| Dirty shutdowns drop requests | `server.close` on SIGTERM/SIGINT |
| Secrets / config in code | Read from `process.env`, never hardcode |

