The current file is quite minimal (23 lines, 2 endpoints), but even this small surface area has several gaps worth addressing. Below are prioritized suggestions.

## 1. Missing error handling infrastructure

**Issues:**
- No global error-handling middleware — any thrown error will produce an unhelpful default Express response (and can leak stack traces in dev).
