## 1. No global error handling
Express will swallow unhandled errors and may leak stack traces in default responses.

**Suggestion:** add an error-handling middleware and a 404 handler at the end of the route chain.
```js
// 404 for unmatched routes
app.use((req, res) => res.status(404).json({ error: 'Not Found' }));

// Centralized error handler — must have 4 args
