1. Add global error handler + 404 (biggest info-leak risk today).
2. Guard `app.listen` behind `require.main === module`.
3. Add `helmet`, body size limit, rate limiter.
4. Add a validation library before the next parameterized route lands.
5. Add auth + PII filtering on `/users`.
6. Graceful shutdown + structured logging.

